General.Name: Ramelius Resources Limited
General.Description: Ramelius Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration, mine development and operation, and sale of gold in Australia. It also offers milling services. The company holds interest in the Mt Magnet mine located within the north-south striking Meekatharra-Mt Magnet greenstone belt of the Western Australian Murchison Province; and Kathleen Valley and Vivien mine located in Western Australia. It also holds interest in various development projects located in Western Australia; and exploration projects located in Western Australia, and New South Wales. Ramelius Resources Limited is headquartered in East Perth, Australia.
